These are Puzzles for 3x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, dutch, russian, brazilian
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, december, july, september
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, sprite, 7up, milk
1. the person drinking juice is the brazilian##1
2. the person drinking 7up is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
5. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left or right of the french##3
6. the person drinking milk is on the left of the russian##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person drinking milk is between the person who's birthday is in september and the french##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |   2    |    3    |     4     |
| Nationality         | brazilian      | french | dutch | russian |
| Birthday   | july | april  | december   | september    |
| Beverage     | juice     | 7up    | milk    | sprite      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, orange, coral, purple
4 different games are played: monopoly, chess, go, domino
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: baccarat, dunhill, swisher, bluemaster
1. the dunhill-smoker is on the left or right of the person who likes coral##3
2. the person who likes purple is the person playing go##1
3. the person who likes coral is in an even position##4
4. the baccarat-smoker is on the far right##1
5. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far left##1
6. the person who likes orange is on the left of the person playing chess##1
7. the person playing monopoly is between the person who likes purple and the person who likes orange##2
8. the person playing domino is between the person playing chess and the person who likes coral##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Color         | purple | coral   | orange | white  |
| Game   | go     | monopoly | domino  | chess |
| Cigar     | bluemaster        | swisher  | dunhill    | baccarat |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, pall-mall, ritmeester, dunhill
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, mystery, thriller, family
House: victorian, colonial, wooden, cape-cod
1. the person watching family movies is between the fonseca-smoker and the dunhill-smoker##2
2. the person watching mystery movies is the cape-cod house##1
3. the victorian house is the ritmeester-smoker##1
4. the victorian house is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is in an odd position##4
6. the person watching thriller movies is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person watching sports movies##2
7. the person watching family movies is on the left of the wooden house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Cigar          | fonseca | pall-mall   | dunhill     | ritmeester     |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery  | family | thriller   | sports  |
| House     | cape-cod      | colonial | wooden | victorian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-4::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, scooter, motorbike, bus
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, italian, brazilian, malaysian
There are 4 different favourite beverages: mirinda, almond-milk, lemonade, coffee
1. the malaysian is in an even position##4
2. the person driving the scooter is the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the italian is on the left or right of the person driving the motorbike##3
5. the malaysian is the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is the dutch##1
7. the brazilian is the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Transport   | roller  | bus   | motorbike     | scooter |
| Nationality   | brazilian  | malaysian      | dutch        | italian     |
| Beverage         | lemonade | mirinda | coffee | almond-milk   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, 7up, almond-milk, iced-tea
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, avocado, strawberry, cabbage
House: art-deco, modern, gothic-revival, tower
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the person eating cabbage##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an odd position##4
3. the art-deco house is the person eating cabbage##1
4. the modern house is on the left of the person eating cabbage##1
5. the art-deco house is in an even position##4
6. the person eating avocado is on the far left##1
7. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the gothic-revival house##3
9. the person eating eggplant is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |    4     |
| Beverage   | sprite   | iced-tea   | almond-milk | 7up |
| Food         | avocado      | cabbage | eggplant      | strawberry |
| House     | modern | art-deco        | tower       | gothic-revival  |

