.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-6::.
House: cape-cod, victorian, art-deco, ranch-style
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, epic, satire, disaster
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, car, subway
1. the victorian house is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the car is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
3. the person driving the airplane is the victorian house##1
4. the art-deco house is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
5. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
6. the ranch-style house is on the left of the victorian house##1
7. the ranch-style house is in an even position##4
8. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person watching zombie movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |     3      |    4    |
| House    | art-deco   | ranch-style      | victorian       | cape-cod |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | disaster | satire     | epic |
| Transport     | subway     | jet-ski  | airplane | car |

