.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-7::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, coach, accountant, social-worker
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, amber, fuchsia, orange
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, british, italian, american
1. the italian is the person who likes apricot##1
2. the british is between the person who likes orange and the indonesian##2
3. the person who likes orange is the coach##1
4. the person who likes amber is on the left or right of the coach##3
5. the security-guard is in an even position##4
6. the person who likes orange is on the right of the social-worker##1
7. the person who likes apricot is the security-guard##1
8. the italian is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |       3       |     4      |
| Job      | accountant   | social-worker          | coach | security-guard        |
| Color   | fuchsia     | amber | orange   | apricot     |
| Nationality           | indonesian | british         | american         | italian |

