.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, 7up, mirinda, iced-tea
There are 4 different nationalities: italian, indonesian, spanish, canadian
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, pony, dog, mouse
1. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the dog##3
2. the spanish is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
3. the canadian is the person drinking mirinda##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
5. the owner of the pony is between the italian and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
6. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the spanish##3
7. the person drinking hot-chocolate is in an even position##4
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking mirinda##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |     4      |
| Beverage         | 7up | hot-chocolate      | mirinda       | iced-tea    |
| Nationality           | indonesian  | spanish  | canadian | italian |
| Pet   | mouse      | dog | pony         | hedgehog    |

