.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-9::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: october, april, june, january
City: venice, liverpool, hannover, paris
There 4 different types of food: pepper, peas, broccoli, kale
1. the person traveling to venice is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
3. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left or right of the person traveling to venice##3
4. the person eating peas is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
5. the person who's birthday is in april is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
7. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
8. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
9. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |      3       |       4       |
| Birthday   | april         | october  | june     | january         |
| City        | paris | liverpool | venice | hannover         |
| Food      | peas         | broccoli  | pepper   | kale |

