.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: light-blue, orange, blood-red, green
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: april, march, june, september
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, cooking, sudoku, photography
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left or right of the person who likes blood-red##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in april is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who likes orange##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who likes orange and the person who likes light-blue##2
 5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who likes orange##3
 6. the person who's hobby is photography is the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far right##1
 8. the person who likes light-blue is in an odd position##4
 9. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person who likes green and the person who likes blood-red##2
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Color   | light-blue  | blood-red    | orange | green    |
| Birthday   | april | june | march  | september |
| Hobby           | sudoku   | photography    | woodworking        | cooking   |

