.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-11::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, sunflower, daisy, amaryllis
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, bike, roller, car
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, radish, papaya, peas
1. the person who growspoppy is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person eating peas is on the left or right of the person driving the roller##3
4. the person driving the bike is in an even position##4
5. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
6. the person eating peas is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
7. the person eating radish is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
8. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
9. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |         1          |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Flower      | poppy                | amaryllis  | sunflower | daisy   |
| Transport           | car | bike | helicopter   | roller |
| Food   | radish         | strawberry     | peas     | papaya |

