.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-12::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: poppy, tulip, zinnia, daisy
4 different games are played: mah-jongg, poker, scrabble, go
The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, motorbike, snowmobile, helicopter
1. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left of the person playing poker##1
5. the person driving the ship is between the person playing go and the person driving the helicopter##2
6. the person playing scrabble is in an even position##4
7. the person who growspoppy is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |   3    |    4    |
| Flower          | zinnia    | tulip  | daisy  | poppy |
| Game   | go | poker | mah-jongg | scrabble |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | ship     | helicopter    | motorbike |

