.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-13::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lavender, mauve, amber
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, april, october, june
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, subway, helicopter, scooter
1. the person driving the subway is between the person who likes mauve and the person who's birthday is in september##2
2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
4. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person driving the scooter is in an odd position##4
6. the person who likes lavender is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
7. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in june##3
8. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who likes fuchsia##1
9. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person driving the helicopter and the person driving the van##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3    |     4     |
| Color      | fuchsia | mauve      | lavender  | amber    |
| Birthday   | october   | april | june | september |
| Transport           | scooter      | helicopter       | subway   | van      |

