.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-14::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, lavender, light-blue, yellow
The people have 4 different jobs:  security-guard, pilot, engineer, mechanic
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, tea, coffee, almond-milk
1. the person who likes light-blue is in an even position##4
2. the person who likes lavender is between the person who likes yellow and the person drinking juice##2
3. the person drinking tea is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who likes yellow is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
6. the mechanic is between the person drinking juice and the security-guard##2
7. the person drinking tea is on the far right##1
8. the pilot is in an even position##4
9. the person drinking juice is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3     |     4      |
| Color         | fuchsia    | light-blue | lavender  | yellow  |
| Job   | engineer | pilot       | mechanic | security-guard |
| Beverage         | coffee   | juice      | almond-milk | tea       |

