4. the person traveling to hamburg is the futuristic house##1
5. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1
6. the cape-cod house is the pall-mall-smoker##1
7. the davidoff-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
8. the blend-smoker is the person traveling to prague##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |   4    |
| City      | hamburg      | venice | paris     | prague    |
| House   | futuristic | cape-cod      | ranch-style | palace |
| Cigar           | cain   | pall-mall  | davidoff     | blend |

