.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-16::.
City: venice, prague, marseilles, london
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: marigold, daisy, balloon-flower, rose
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, blues, reggae, salsa
1. the person traveling to venice is on the left or right of the person traveling to prague##3
2. the person who growsmarigold is in an even position##4
3. the fan of salsa is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person traveling to london##3
5. the person traveling to prague is between the fan of blues and the person who growsballoon-flower##2
6. the fan of ambient is the person who growsrose##1
7. the person traveling to prague is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
8. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| City    | marseilles    | prague     | venice    | london        |
| Flower       | balloon-flower   | marigold | daisy | rose |
| Music-Genre   | salsa | reggae      | blues    | ambient   |

