.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-17::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, magic-tricks, reading, woodworking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, lacrosse, snowboarding
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, orchid, sunflower, rose
1. the person who's sport is badminton is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsiris is between the person who growsorchid and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is reading##3
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is in an odd position##4
7. the person who growssunflower is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is woodworking is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |     3     |    4     |
| Hobby          | magic-tricks | woodworking  | writing   | reading    |
| Sport   | basketball  | lacrosse     | snowboarding | badminton |
| Flower   | sunflower   | rose | iris | orchid   |

