5. the person drinking mirinda is the owner of the rabbit##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
7. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
8. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3     |    4     |
