.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  pilot, project-manager, electrician, lawyer
City: hannover, new-york, miami, paris
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, sprite, tea, iced-tea
1. the pilot is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking coffee is on the left or right of the person traveling to hannover##3
4. the electrician is on the far left##1
5. the project-manager is between the person traveling to paris and the person traveling to hannover##2
6. the person traveling to new-york is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
7. the person drinking tea is on the right of the pilot##1
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the project-manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |      2      |   3    |      4      |
| Job    | electrician    | project-manager    | pilot  | lawyer |
| City   | paris | new-york | hannover | miami      |
| Beverage     | sprite   | coffee        | iced-tea   | tea       |

 